<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateGroupNode.StencilTargetFace" Title="StencilTargetFace enumeration" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateGroupNode">IStateGroupNode</PageRef> ->
    StencilTargetFace
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>StencilTargetFace</TypeRef> enumeration selects which polygon faces receive a stencil operation configuration when <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateGroupNode.SetStencilOperation">SetStencilOperation</PageRef> is called.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Members">
    <EnumMemberList>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="FrontFace">
        Applies the stencil operation configuration to front-facing polygons.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="BackFace">
        Applies the stencil operation configuration to back-facing polygons.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="FrontAndBackFace">
        Applies the stencil operation configuration to both front-facing and back-facing polygons.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
    </EnumMemberList>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateGroupNode.SetStencilOperation">IStateGroupNode.SetStencilOperation</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
